<%
var title = 'Refund Policy';
var activePage = 'refund';
%>

<div class="card">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h2 class="fw-bold" style="background: var(--primary-gradient); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">
            <i class="fas fa-undo-alt me-2"></i>Refund Policy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="alert alert-info mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                <strong>Important:</strong> This refund policy is designed to be fair to both our customers and our business while complying with Paddle's merchant requirements.
            </div>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3">1. Overview</h3>
            <p>We want you to be satisfied with our Bulk Email Verifier service. This Refund Policy outlines the circumstances under which refunds may be issued for credit purchases made through our platform.</p>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">2. Refund Eligibility</h3>
            
            <h4 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2">Eligible for Refund:</h4>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Service Outage:</strong> If our service is unavailable for more than 24 consecutive hours</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Technical Issues:</strong> Systematic errors affecting verification accuracy for more than 48 hours</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Duplicate Charges:</strong> Accidental multiple payments for the same credit package</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Billing Errors:</strong> Charges that don't match your intended purchase</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Fraudulent Activity:</strong> Unauthorized charges on your account</li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2 mt-3">Not Eligible for Refund:</h4>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2"></i><strong>Used Credits:</strong> Credits that have been consumed for email verification</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2"></i><strong>Change of Mind:</strong> Simple change of mind after successful purchase</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2"></i><strong>Expired Credits:</strong> Credits that have passed their 12-month expiration date</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2"></i><strong>User Error:</strong> Mistakes in uploading or formatting email lists</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2"></i><strong>Third-party Issues:</strong> Problems with external email servers or domains</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">3. Refund Timeframes</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="alert alert-light border">
                        <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2"><i class="fas fa-clock text-warning me-2"></i>Request Window</h5>
                        <p class="mb-0">Refund requests must be submitted within <strong>30 days</strong> of the original purchase date.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="alert alert-light border">
                        <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2"><i class="fas fa-hourglass-half text-info me-2"></i>Processing Time</h5>
                        <p class="mb-0">Approved refunds are processed within <strong>5-10 business days</strong> via the original payment method.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">4. Partial Refunds</h3>
            <p>In certain circumstances, we may offer partial refunds:</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-percentage text-info me-2"></i><strong>Unused Credits:</strong> Refund for unused credits if significant service issues occurred</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-percentage text-info me-2"></i><strong>Service Degradation:</strong> Proportional refund if service quality was substantially reduced</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-percentage text-info me-2"></i><strong>Account Termination:</strong> Refund for unused credits if we terminate your account for reasons other than violation of terms</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">5. How to Request a Refund</h3>
            <div class="card border-primary">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane text-primary me-2"></i>Refund Request Process</h5>
                    <ol class="mb-0">
                        <li class="mb-2">Contact our support team through the <a href="/support" class="text-decoration-none" style="color: #667eea;">Support page</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Provide your account email and order/transaction ID</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Clearly explain the reason for your refund request</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Include any relevant documentation or screenshots</li>
                        <li class="mb-0">Wait for our team to review and respond within 2 business days</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">6. Credit Expiration Policy</h3>
            <div class="alert alert-warning">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                <strong>Important:</strong> All purchased credits expire 12 months from the date of purchase. Expired credits are not eligible for refund.
            </div>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt text-warning me-2"></i>You will receive email reminders 30 days and 7 days before expiration</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-bell text-info me-2"></i>Check your account dashboard regularly for credit balance and expiration dates</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-clock text-secondary me-2"></i>No extensions are provided for expired credits</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">7. Payment Processor Policy</h3>
            <p>All payments are processed by Paddle, our secure payment partner. Refunds are subject to Paddle's terms and conditions:</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-success me-2"></i>Refunds are processed through the same payment method used for purchase</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-credit-card text-info me-2"></i>Bank processing times may vary (typically 3-10 business days)</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-globe text-secondary me-2"></i>International transactions may have additional processing time</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">8. Dispute Resolution</h3>
            <p>If you disagree with our refund decision:</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-comments text-primary me-2"></i>Contact our support team to discuss the matter further</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-escalator text-warning me-2"></i>Request escalation to our management team</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-balance-scale text-info me-2"></i>Consider mediation through Paddle's dispute resolution process</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">9. Service Credits vs. Monetary Refunds</h3>
            <p>In some cases, we may offer service credits instead of monetary refunds:</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-coins text-warning me-2"></i><strong>Service Credits:</strong> Additional verification credits added to your account</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-plus-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Bonus Credits:</strong> Extra credits as compensation for inconvenience</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-calendar-plus text-info me-2"></i><strong>Extended Expiration:</strong> Extended validity period for existing credits</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">10. Subscription Cancellations</h3>
            <p>If we introduce subscription plans in the future:</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-stop-circle text-danger me-2"></i>Subscriptions can be cancelled at any time</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check text-info me-2"></i>No pro-rated refunds for current billing periods</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-ban text-warning me-2"></i>Access continues until the end of the current billing cycle</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">11. Changes to Refund Policy</h3>
            <p>We reserve the right to modify this Refund Policy at any time. Material changes will be communicated via:</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-envelope text-primary me-2"></i>Email notification to registered users</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-bullhorn text-warning me-2"></i>Notice on our website and service dashboard</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-calendar text-info me-2"></i>30-day advance notice for significant changes</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3 mt-4">12. Contact Information</h3>
            <p>For any questions about this Refund Policy or to request a refund, please contact our support team through the <a href="/support" class="text-decoration-none" style="color: #667eea;">Support page</a>.</p>

            <div class="alert alert-success mt-4">
                <i class="fas fa-handshake me-2"></i>
                <strong>Our Commitment:</strong> We strive to provide excellent service and will work with you to resolve any legitimate concerns about your purchase in a fair and timely manner.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>